import React, { useState } from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import {
  Navbar,
  LogoContainer,
  Logo,
  Navigation,
  Dropdown,
  HomeLink,
  DropdownBox,
  DropdownContainer,
  DropdownOption
} from './NavigatorStyles'

import LogoIcon from '../images/pubg.png'

export default function Navigator({ handleClick }) {
  const [toggle, setToggle] = useState(false)

  const handleToggle = () => {
    setToggle(!toggle)
  }

  return (
    <Navbar>
      <Link to="/">
        <LogoContainer>
          <Logo src={LogoIcon} />
        </LogoContainer>
      </Link>
      <Navigation>
        <Link to="/" className="link">
          <HomeLink>Home</HomeLink>
        </Link>
        <Dropdown onClick={() => handleToggle()}>
          Leaderboards
          <i className="fas fa-caret-down" />
        </Dropdown>
        <DropdownBox show={toggle}>
          <DropdownOption>Duo</DropdownOption>
          <DropdownOption>Duo FPP</DropdownOption>
          <DropdownOption>Solo</DropdownOption>
          <DropdownOption>Solo FPP</DropdownOption>
          <DropdownOption>Squad</DropdownOption>
          <DropdownOption>Squad FPP</DropdownOption>
        </DropdownBox>
      </Navigation>
    </Navbar>
  )
}
